                    <article class="blog-post ios-card" data-category="design-notes">
                        <div class="post-header">
                            <span class="post-category">设计笔记</span>
                            <h2>跨平台动效参数转换指南：从 Origami 到原生实现</h2>
                            <p class="post-subtitle">深入解析各平台弹性动效参数及其转换方法</p>
                            <div class="post-meta">
                                <span class="reading-time">阅读时间 8 分钟</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="post-content">
                            <div class="intro-block">
                                <p class="highlight">在跨平台产品开发中，如何准确地将设计工具中的动效参数转换为各平台的原生实现，是一个常见的技术挑战。本文将详细介绍 Origami、iOS、Android 等平台的动效参数转换方法。</p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="section-block">
                                <h3>一、参数对照表</h3>
                                <div class="params-grid">
                                    <div class="param-card">
                                        <h4>🎨 Origami Studio</h4>
                                        <div class="param-group">
                                            <h5>Pop Animation:</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Bounciness: 弹性程度</li>
                                                <li>Speed: 效果快慢</li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <h5>Bouncy Converter:</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Friction: 摩擦力</li>
                                                <li>Tension: 张力</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="param-card">
                                        <h4>📱 iOS</h4>
                                        <div class="param-group">
                                            <h5>UIViewSpring:</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>dampingRatio: 阻尼比</li>
                                                <li>duration: 持续时间</li>
                                                <li>velocity: 初始速度</li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <h5>CASpringAnimation:</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>damping: 阻尼</li>
                                                <li>stiffness: 刚度</li>
                                                <li>mass: 质量</li>
                                                <li>initialVelocity: 初始速度</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="param-card">
                                        <h4>🤖 Android</h4>
                                        <div class="param-group">
                                            <h5>SpringAnimation:</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>dampingRatio: 阻尼比</li>
                                                <li>stiffness: 刚度</li>
                                                <li>startVelocity: 初始速度</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="section-block">
                                <h3>二、参数转换公式</h3>
                                <div class="formula-block">
                                    <pre class="code-block">
damping = friction
stiffness = tension
mass = 1 (默认值)
dampingRatio = damping / (2 * sqrt(mass * stiffness))
velocity = 0 (默认值)</pre>
                                </div>

                                <div class="example-block">
                                    <h4>🔄 转换示例</h4>
                                    <p>当 Origami Pop Animation 参数为：</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Bounciness = 5</li>
                                        <li>Speed = 10</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>转换后得到：</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Friction = 27.0487</li>
                                        <li>Tension = 299.61884</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>最终各平台实现参数：</p>
                                    <div class="code-tabs">
                                        <div class="code-tab">
                                            <h5>Android Implementation</h5>
                                            <pre class="code-block">
SpringAnimation(object, DynamicAnimation.[property]).apply {
    spring.dampingRatio = 0.78f
    spring.stiffness = 299.62f
    setStartVelocity(0f)
}</pre>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="code-tab">
                                            <h5>iOS Implementation</h5>
                                            <pre class="code-block">
let spring = CASpringAnimation(keyPath: [property])
spring.stiffness = 299.62
spring.damping = 27.05
spring.mass = 1
spring.initialVelocity = 0</pre>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="section-block">
                                <h3>三、Android 兼容性解决方案</h3>
                                <p>对于 Android X 以下版本，可以使用自定义插值器实现类似效果：</p>
                                <pre class="code-block">
public class SpringInterpolator extends BaseInterpolator {
    private float mFactor;

    public SpringInterpolator() {
        this.mFactor = 0.5f;
    }

    public SpringInterpolator(float mFactor) {
        this.mFactor = mFactor;
    }

    @Override
    public float getInterpolation(float input) {
        if (input == 0.0f || input == 1.0f)
            return input;
        else {
            float value = (float) (Math.pow(2, -10 * input) * 
                Math.sin((input - mFactor / 4.0d) * (2.0d * Math.PI) / mFactor) + 1);
            return value;
        }
    }
}</pre>
                            </div>

                            <div class="section-block">
                                <h3>四、实践建议</h3>
                                <div class="tips-block">
                                    <ul class="styled-list">
                                        <li>优先使用 Origami Studio 进行动效原型设计，其参数转换最为完整</li>
                                        <li>注意不同平台的参数单位可能存在差异，需要进行相应调整</li>
                                        <li>对于复杂动效，建议创建可复用的动效组件</li>
                                        <li>在低端 Android 设备上，使用插值器方案可以获得更好的兼容性</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>

